Class Member

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class Member extends Object implements Comparable<Member>
This class represents a generic member of the fitness club. Serves as a super class for different types of memberships (Basic, Family, Premium)
Author:
